### Configuracoes Iniciais (Variaveis)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 0. Login para obter token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "contato@opticaflow.com.br",
  "senha": "11222333000181"
}

###

@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN
@empresaId = COLE_ID_EMPRESA
@laboratorioId = COLE_ID_LABORATORIO

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------
### LABORATORIO
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Criar laboratorio
POST {{baseUrl}}/laboratorio
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "nome": "Laboratorio Vision Prime",
  "cnpj": "12345678000199",
  "email": "contato@visionprime.com.br",
  "telefone": "11999998888",
  "ativo": true
}

### 2. Listar laboratorios por empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/laboratorio/empresa/{{empresaId}}?page=1&limit=10&search=vision&ativo=true
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Buscar laboratorio por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/laboratorio/{{laboratorioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Atualizar laboratorio
PUT {{baseUrl}}/laboratorio/{{laboratorioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nome": "Laboratorio Vision Prime Plus",
  "email": "suporte@visionprime.com.br",
  "ativo": true
}

### 5. Teste negativo: nome duplicado na mesma empresa
POST {{baseUrl}}/laboratorio
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "nome": "Laboratorio Vision Prime Plus"
}

### 6. Deletar laboratorio (somente sem ordens de servico vinculadas)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/laboratorio/{{laboratorioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
